INSERT INTO `sep_posts` VALUES (340,1,'2014-05-22 02:29:24','2014-05-22 02:29:24','<p><a target=\"_blank\" title=\"Kids in the House website\" href=\"http://kidsinthehouse.com\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-222\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" alt=\"kidsinthehouse\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/kidsinthehouse1.jpg\" height=\"250\" width=\"521\" width=\"521\" height=\"250\" /></a></p> <p>Dr. Levine has agreed to take part in a shoot this Thursday for <a target=\"_blank\" title=\"Kids in the hosue home page\" href=\"http://kidsinthehouse.com\">Kidsinthehouse.com</a>, a online video resource for parents that is designed to offer searchable, quick results from professionals and fellow parents alike. We invite you to check out their site, (which is still under development) and sign up for future news. We have been given access to the early beta, and the footage is amazing. With the vast amount of content there, we are sure that this website will definitely be of immense help to parents everywhere. Peter\'s co-author, Maggie Kline, will also be featured. Head on to their website and check out the Sizzle Reel.</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p>','Kids in the House - Resources for Parents','','inherit','open','open','','223-revision-v1','','','2014-05-22 02:29:24','2014-05-22 02:29:24','',223,'http://localhost:8888/speed/223-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `sep_posts` VALUES (341,1,'2014-05-22 02:29:24','2014-05-22 02:29:24','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-218\" src=\"http://somaticexperiencing.com/export/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/SD_Case_Consult.jpg\" width=\"671\" height=\"303\" alt=\"SD Case Consult\" style=\"border: 2px solid #2b84c8; padding: 2px;\" width=\"671\" height=\"303\" /></p> <p>The SE® Trauma Institute is privileged to offer a day of case consultations and supervision with author and founder of the Somatic Experiencing® trauma resolution model, Peter A. Levine, PhD.&nbsp;</p> <p>Open to Therapists using body focused approaches, body workers, chiropractors, acupuncturists, nurses, etc. and open to training participants and practitioners of Somatic Experiencing®. The Day is geared for Intermediate students or above, however, Beginners are welcome to present a case or ask questions. Each three hours of consultation time equals one hour credit toward the required eighteen hours for SEP certification. <strong>Remember to bring your session log to receive SEP credit.&nbsp;</strong></p> <blockquote> <p><em>\"This is an ideal opportunity to observe Peter modeling his highly creative, intelligent and sensitve healing skills in an intimate and comfortable environment. His demonstrations and explantions furthered my understanding of the myriad of compleixties and simplicities of Somatic Experiencing®. This last supervision with Peter was unforgettable, profound, inspiring and a very encouraging experience for me as a practitioner.\" </em>Victoria Mihich, MA, MFT, SEP</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;<a href=\"index.php?option=com_eventbooking&amp;view=category&amp;Itemid=110\" title=\"Event Page\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>You can register by clicking here.</strong></span></a></p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <ul> <li><a href=\"https://somaticexperiencing.com/events/consult-registration.html?task=view_event&amp;event_id=16\" title=\"All Day Signup\">All Day Registration</a>: (11am-6pm, worth 2 Consult Hours)<span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong></strong></span></li> <li><a href=\"https://somaticexperiencing.com/events/consult-registration.html?task=view_event&amp;event_id=14\" title=\"Afternoon Signup\">Afternoon (2nd half) Registration</a>: (3pm-6pm, worth 1 Consult Hour)</li> <li><a href=\"https://somaticexperiencing.com/events/consult-registration.html?task=view_event&amp;event_id=15\" title=\"Morning Sign Up\">Morning (1st Half) Registration</a>:&nbsp;(11am-2pm, worth 1 Consult Hour)</li> </ul> <p><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">Please contact Joan Luly for </span><a href=\"http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/caseconsultflyer1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">more information</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">: </span><a href=\"mailto:joansehealing@mac.com\" style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">joansehealing@mac.com</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">.</span></p> <p><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\"><a href=\"http://somaticexperiencing.com/export/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/may11.13reg_consult.pdf\" title=\"Registration form and Check\" target=\"_blank\">Snail Mail Option</a>.&nbsp;</span></p> <p><a href=\"http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/peter_case_consult_san_diego_may1120131.pdf\" title=\"Event Flyer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">Also, the Flier</span></a></p> <p>If you are interested in having Peter see a client of yours, please contact Justin Snavely at <a href=\"mailto:traumahealing@gmail.com\">traumahealing@gmail.com</a>&nbsp;with the following information:</p> <ol> <li>First name and age of client.</li> <li>Brief list of relevant trauma history (Including the age that it occurred)</li> <li>Ways in which therapy is stuck.</li> <li>Ways in which therapy is advancing.</li> <li>Why do you specifically want Peter to see this client.&nbsp;</li> </ol> <p>NOTE: NO cancellations can be made after May 8th, 2013. Thank you.&nbsp;</p> </blockquote>','Peter Levine Group Case Consultation in San Diego - May 11th!','','inherit','open','open','','221-revision-v1','','','2014-05-22 02:29:24','2014-05-22 02:29:24','',221,'http://localhost:8888/speed/221-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `sep_posts` VALUES (342,1,'2014-05-22 02:29:24','2014-05-22 02:29:24','It is the sincere honor of SomaticExperiencing.com to announce the release of Freedom From Pain. This program (both a standalone 2-disc Audio album and Book/CD) to not just show the links between Chronic Pain and trauma, but to provide sufferers with a \"toolbox\" of techniques, exercises and resources to create a custom treatment system for tackling this complex and widespread issue. Written by Dr. Levine, and his long time collaborator, colleague, SE® faculty member, and pain expert, Dr. Maggie Phillips, this is the culmination of 75 years of combined clinical experience, as well as 5 years of collaboration and feedback from countless seminars and therapists. Now these tried and true techniques are available to everyone.  Granted, we are getting to this story a bit late, as this book has been on the shelves for several months now. But the reception that we have received from what friends who have given the book and audio series out have said, to emails from caring fans, has been exceptionally positive. THey have all reported that symptomology has reduced greatly, and that friends, clients, and themselves are finding long-lasting, significant relief, which makes us exceptionally happy here.','Freedom From Pain - ','','inherit','open','open','','215-revision-v1','','','2014-05-22 02:29:24','2014-05-22 02:29:24','',215,'http://localhost:8888/speed/215-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `sep_posts` VALUES (343,1,'2014-05-22 02:29:24','2014-05-22 02:29:24','<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://player.vimeo.com/video/54418002\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe></div> <p>Next Friday, Dr. Levine will participate on a live panel, as part of a tele-symposim to bring awareness to the effects of human trafficking, which is a $32-billion industry worldwide. Be part of an event to raise awareness. <a href=\"http://magnificentminded.com/mission/mission-to-mind-health/\" title=\"Mission to mind home page\" target=\"_blank\">Listen live or listen the recordings</a>. The press release is after the break.&nbsp;</p> <p><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p> <p><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;\"></span></b></p>  <!--more-->  <p><b>Do You Know What It Takes to Make a Lifestyle Lift?</b></p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\"><span>If you would like to find out...</span></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\"><span>This free 4-part tele and web summit has been created to help people become the master of their own magnificence by enriching the mind and enhancing practices <i>and I am sharing my expertise related to –</i></span></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\"><span>Mission to Mind Health Mastery is a free 4-part, 26 hour tele and video symposium with the goal for you to discover <b>Maximum&nbsp; - Peace Potential Performance and Prosperity</b></span></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\"><span>Why is this important?</span></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\"><span>Well, our experiences can shape and structure our brains and this, in turn plays a powerful role in moulding our stories.&nbsp; We want you to have the power to create your story with rich possibilities.</span></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\"><span>Carol Soares has gathered 45 of the best brain/mind health, personal growth and transformation experts in the world for this event which continues on Friday, February 15 @ 11 am (EST). &nbsp;The focus is performance – how you interact with and “show up” in the world. Visit </span><span><a href=\"http://missiontomindmastery.com\"></a><a href=\"http://missiontomindmastery.com\">http://missiontomindmastery.com</a></span><span> to listen to the amazing interviews. It truly is a mind marathon focusing on many aspects of wellness! The day will include a series of 8 incredible 25-minute interviews that will help you to take away nuggets provided in small portions for applying to your daily life.&nbsp; Our collaborative mission is for the world to be equipped to tap into the power of their magnificence. That includes you!</span></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\"><span>The mission aims to have you take away a minimum of 50 ways to fortify your mind for maximum possibilities (that you can start using immediately). This information will not only help you to optimize your mind, but because Carol is specifically dedicating the event to women/mompreneurs, if you are a woman, you’re going to take this to enrich your life, family and social life, and your business.&nbsp; </span></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\"><span>By connecting through this event you will also help raise awareness and support for My Refuge House for girls who are survivors of sex trafficking experiences.&nbsp; The numbers of women and children affected continues to be astounding. </span></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\"><span>Human trafficking is a criminal business that profits from enslaving people for sexual servitude and forced labor.</span><span> It is the fastest growing and second largest criminal industry in the world today. Human trafficking is a $32-billion industry worldwide.</span></p> <p><span>Listen live or listen the recordings. It’s up to you. We just hope that you make your personal growth a priority and listen. Register here: </span><a href=\"http: