INSERT INTO `sep_posts` VALUES (392,1,'2014-05-22 02:31:30','2014-05-22 02:31:30','<p>Everyone has questions about trauma, what it is, and how to get help. Unfortunately, Peter can\'t guide everyone. It is unethical for him to give case consultations or advice to anyone that he is not directly related to. If you are looking for help with a trauma issue, we recommend that you find a Somatic Experiencing Practitioner (SEP) in your area, please see the <a href=\"http://www.traumahealing.com/somatic-experiencing/practitioner-directory.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Find a Practitioner\">Practitioners Registry</a> at the traumahealing website for the Foundation for Human Enrichment, a non-profit organization started by Peter, to oversee the training of therapists in his techniques. <br /><br /></p>','I have a question about trauma, can you help?','','inherit','open','open','','145-revision-v1','','','2014-05-22 02:31:30','2014-05-22 02:31:30','',145,'http://localhost:8888/speed/145-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `sep_posts` VALUES (393,1,'2014-05-22 02:31:30','2014-05-22 02:31:30','<p>Unfortunately, due to his current time constraints, he is unable to see private clients. However, he has 5,000 people training in Somatic Experiencing globally, and the best way is to check out the <a href=\"http://www.traumahealing.com/somatic-experiencing/practitioner-directory.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Find a Practitioner\">Practitioners Registry</a> There are still chances to see him by checking out his events page.</p>','Does Peter see private clients?','','inherit','open','open','','144-revision-v1','','','2014-05-22 02:31:30','2014-05-22 02:31:30','',144,'http://localhost:8888/speed/144-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
